      }
    }
  }
}
```
In this example, the `posts` collection can be read by anyone but written only by the authenticated user with the `admin` claim. The rules also ensure that the `title` and `content` fields are validated before they are written to the database. The `users` collection can be read and written only by the authenticated user with the corresponding UID.

